<div class="title">Best ADHD Medication I Have Tried</div>
<div class="substance">Lisdexamphetamine (Vyvanse)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=ADHD+Momma&Exact=1">ADHD Momma</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; ADHD Momma. "Best ADHD Medication I Have Tried: An Experience with Lisdexamphetamine (Vyvanse) (exp81479)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 30, 2010. erowid.org/exp/81479</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
